Rating: 4
This was a great app for a cocktail party last night. Made the remoulade the night before and all the flavors blended nicely. Doubled the shrimp and added a few hours before serving. The mixture was tight enough to top the toasts without being runny. The westphalian toasts did not add a distinct flavor for me, perhaps I didn't use enough of the butter mixture. I'm willing to give the toasts another shot but the shrimp could easily be served on plain toasted baguette and be just as good. Oh, forgot the chives for the top and didn't miss them. I scraped the leftover shrimp off of the toasts and am enjoying it on a piece of Naan as a wrap for lunch. Delish!

