Rating: 4
This is fabulous, but there is an even better Remlaude Sauce from Bon Appetit many years ago. Unfortunately, it isn't a recipe that they posted, but here it is....just mix everything in the blender: 3 chopped scallions 3 Tbs creole mustard ¼ cup ketchup 1 Tbs American yellow mustard 2 Tbs white vinegar 3 Tbs drained horseradish 2 Tbs parsley 1 tsp minced garlic 1 ½ tsp lemon juice 2 tsp creole seasoning ¼ tsp tobasco 1 ½ tsp paprika dash cayenne ½ tsp salt ¼ cup olive oil *can be made three days ahead

